#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
msgid "There are 2 ways of shutting down Tails."
msgstr "有幾種方式可以關閉 Tails:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toc levels=1]]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"With both techniques, all the data stored in [[!wikipedia Random-access_memory\n"
"desc=\"RAM\"]] is securely erased to protect you from [[cold boot\n"
"attacks|doc/advanced_topics/cold_boot_attacks]].\n"
msgstr ""
"關閉時，儲存在 <span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia_zh \n"
"Random-Access_Memory desc=\"RAM\"]]</span>的資料會被抹除， 以防備來自\n"
"[[冷開機|doc/advanced_topics/cold_boot_attacks]] 攻擊。\n"

